other_tests.findings: The appendix was dilated up to 1.2 cm with periappendiceal fat stranding consistent with acute appendicitis; a 3 mm appendicolith was identified.
The CT showed a dilated appendix up to 1.2 cm, a 3 mm appendicolith, and periappendiceal fat stranding. No free intra-abdominal air was observed.
